## USER PAIN POINTS & RESEARCH

### Top 5 Pain Points
1. **"Too many options, don't know which kit to buy"** - Overwhelmed by 50+ kits on Amazon, want clear recommendations by price/skill level
2. **"Will the colors actually match what I see online?"** - Concern about gel polish colors looking different in person, want swatch accuracy
3. **"Is it actually cheaper than salon or will I waste money?"** - Budget anxiety, need cost breakdown showing break-even point vs salon visits
4. **"What if I mess it up - is it beginner friendly?"** - Fear of ruining nails, need reassurance about learning curve and mistakes
5. **"How long will it actually last before chipping?"** - Durability concerns, want honest longevity expectations (not marketing hype)

### User Sentiment
Excited but cautious - users love the idea of DIY Valentine nails but worried about wasting money on wrong kit or getting frustrated with application

